description: Pheonix calls Ricky in to be a company personal trainer and finds out how great he is at foot worship. First Ricky relaxes Pheonix my massaging his feet and sniffing his dress socks. Then Ricky worships the dress socks and the boss’ masculine bare feet. Pheonix loves it of course and soon his company has a new employee.
title: Boss Pheonix Foot Worshiped
